BAUCHI – Former Speaker of the House of Representatives, Yakubu Dogara, Chief of Air Staff (COAS), Sadiq Abubakar, Deputy Controller General Nigeria Custom Service, Abdullahi T. Babani and a member Bauchi State House of Assembly, Dan’umma Bello Giade, have bagged Excellence Award 2020 by an organization known as the Bauchi Unity Group. Others are: Hon Abdulrazak Nuhu Zaki, Hon Ja’afar Leko, Hon Naira Mano Soro and Dr Abubakar Surumbai Sheik Tahir. The Chairman of the Bauchi Unity Group, Hon Garba Audi Garkuwan Kundum, said that the organization gave the award in recognition of the recipients efforts at improving the quality of lives of people around them in the state, promoting quality leadership and modeling leaders. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! He said that the Bauchi Unity Group is an Organization whose membership cut cross all political and religious groups, adding that the group was founded 30 years ago with the vision of giving honour to prominent personalities in the state who has impacted humanity and improved the lives of citizens of the State. He said that this year event was designed to bring together community and government leaders, corporations and foundations to celebrate the best personalities in the state with the aim encouraging others to emulate their good virtues. Finland Confirms First Adverse Reaction To COVID-19 Vaccine Solskjaer Reflects On Man Utd Progress Since Arsenal Loss Amid Liverpool Talk Also in his address at the event, the Secretary Organising Commitee of the Organization, Pastor Shedra Bamayi said that the award ceremony is a yearly event organised to honour well deserved elites from the state in recognition of thier selfless services to the common man in the society, adding that out of 25 nominees, they selected 8 outstanding personalities who performed remarkable well in thier service to the state. “I have the honour of congratulating all the awardees for thier service to humanity, advanced achievements and outstanding personal development.It is our ernest prayer that God in his intimate Mercy will continue to give you the strength, wisdom and protection, thus, contributing to the common man well-being in the state” “Always keep in your mind that the great people of Bauchi State look at you with great expectations and hope to gain a perfect mentor and faithful friend,” he said. The Secretary said that the group has plans to construct a recreation center in the state worth N22 million, thereby reducing youth restiveness in the state. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION